## Risk Acceptance Criteria and Methodology

Risk is scored using the **{{ if .RiskMethod }}{{ .RiskMethod }}{{ else }}qualitative{{ end }}** method. A risk is **accepted** without treatment when its level is one of: {{ range $i, $l := .RiskAccept }}{{ if $i }}, {{ end }}`{{ $l }}`{{ end }}{{ if not .RiskAccept }}(none defined){{ end }}. Any risk above the acceptance criteria must record a treatment decision (mitigate / accept / transfer / avoid) and an owner.

